qtDescription: Get in great shape by doing a combination of some or all of these quickies.
These quickies are the best way to get your feet moving and heart pumping.
Try these beginner level quickies if you are just starting to work out.
Attempt these quickies if you enjoy an extremely difficult challenge.
Bar Quickies are great if you want to challenge yourself with full body weight exercises.
Give these quickies a whirl, if you're a master of calisthenics.
Don't forget to perform some dynamic stretches to get the blood flowing and loosen up your muscles before exercising.
